```plantuml
@startuml nikmis_xentrace-analysis
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
left to right direction

actor "User"

package "Xen Performance Analysis Tool" {
  rectangle "xentrace-analysis.c" as XTraceAnalysis #lightgrey
  rectangle "src/Reader.c" as Reader #lightblue
  rectangle "src/EventHandler.c" as EventHandler #lightgreen
  rectangle "src/Event.c" as Event #lightyellow
  rectangle "include/Trace.h" as Trace #lightpink
  rectangle "examples/*/" as Examples #lightpurple
}

User --> XTraceAnalysis

XTraceAnalysis --> Reader : Launches & manages
Reader --> EventHandler : Distributes parsed events
EventHandler --> Examples : Invokes registered handlers
Reader --> Event : Parses events
Event --> Trace : Uses trace event IDs

Examples <..> "include/list.h" : Uses linked lists

note right of EventHandler
  Event-driven architecture
  - Modular design
  - Observer Pattern
end note

note right of Examples
  Strategy Pattern
  - Different analyses
end note

@enduml
